{"word":"G526 - ἀπαλλοτριόω - apallotrióō - ap-al-lot-ree-o'-o - Alienate","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπαλλοτριόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apallotrióō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-al-lot-ree-o'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Alienate</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - புறம்பானவர், அந்நியர்"},{"paragraph":"to alienate, estrange to be shut out from one's fellowship and intimacy"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G245 - ἀλλότριος - allótrios - al-lot'-ree-os/245\">G245</a>; to <i>estrange away</i>, that is, (passively and figuratively) to <i>be non participant:</i> - alienate, be alien.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G241/241\">G241</a>, <a href=\"#/G243/243\">G243</a>, <a href=\"#/G245/245\">G245</a>, <a href=\"#/G246/246\">G246</a>, <a href=\"#/G526/526\">G526</a>"}]}